    				Columnstore Indexes – part 97 (“Working with Strings”)    			 
  			 
    			 Continuation from the previous 96 parts, the whole series can be found at  http://www.nikoport.com/columnstore/ . 
 After many years of using &amp; fighting the  String  data type in Columnstore Indexes, I have finally decided to write a blog post that is dedicated to them and show some of the cases that I have meet. 
 For the queries I will be using the same version generated copy of the TPCH database (1GB version), that I have used previously. If you want to have one, use the go